### =============================================================================
### ✅ GET — List Card Requests
### =============================================================================

### [1] All requests — default page 1, limit 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [2] Filter by PENDING
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [3] Filter by APPROVED
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests?status=APPROVED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Filter by REJECTED (CANCELLED in DB)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests?status=REJECTED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [5] Search by order number
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests?search=ORD-2025
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [6] Paginated — page 2, limit 5
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests?page=2&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### =============================================================================
### ✅ POST — Submit New Card Request
### =============================================================================

### [7] Valid submission — BLANK order (no student details, school assigns later)
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "card_count": 150,
  "order_type": "BLANK",
  "notes": "Annual re-issuance for new academic session 2025-26. All Class 9 and 10 students require fresh cards.",
  "delivery_name": "Principal Office",
  "delivery_phone": "9876543210",
  "delivery_address": "12, Sector 12, Dwarka",
  "delivery_line2": "Near Metro Station",
  "delivery_city": "New Delhi",
  "delivery_state": "Delhi",
  "delivery_pincode": "110075"
}

###

### [8] Valid submission — PRE_DETAILS order (names/photos on cards)
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "card_count": 80,
  "order_type": "PRE_DETAILS",
  "notes": "Replacement cards for lost/damaged IDs reported in Term 1. Student list will be uploaded separately.",
  "delivery_name": "Admin Block",
  "delivery_phone": "9123456789",
  "delivery_address": "Plot 7, Civil Lines",
  "delivery_city": "Nagpur",
  "delivery_state": "Maharashtra",
  "delivery_pincode": "440001"
}

###

### =============================================================================
### ❌ VALIDATION ERRORS — rejected at middleware, never hits DB
### =============================================================================

### [9] Missing auth — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests
Accept: application/json

###

### [10] Wrong school (tenant mismatch) — expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000/card-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [11] Invalid UUID format — expect 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{badUUID}}/card-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [12] card_count exceeds 300 — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "card_count": 500,
  "order_type": "BLANK",
  "notes": "This should be rejected — over the 300 card limit per request.",
  "delivery_name": "Office",
  "delivery_phone": "9876543210",
  "delivery_address": "123 Main Street",
  "delivery_city": "Mumbai",
  "delivery_state": "Maharashtra",
  "delivery_pincode": "400001"
}

###

### [13] Invalid pincode (not 6 digits) — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/card-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "card_count": 50,
  "order_type": "BLANK",
  "notes": "Testing pincode validation with wrong format.",
  "delivery_name": "Office",
  "delivery_phone": "9876543210",
  "delivery_address": "123 Main Street",
  "delivery_city": "Mumbai",
  "delivery_state": "Maharashtra",
  "delivery_pincode": "1234"
}

###

### [14] Notes too short — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
